{"id":606,"date":"2021-06-04T15:19:25","date_gmt":"2021-06-04T15:19:25","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/joeyfarruggio.com\/?p=606"},"modified":"2021-06-04T15:24:08","modified_gmt":"2021-06-04T15:24:08","slug":"remove-white-background-css","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/joeyfarruggio.com\/wordpress\/remove-white-background-css\/","title":{"rendered":"Remove white background from image \u2013 CSS  solution."},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>So I&#8217;m building a premium WP theme tailored for Affiliates and product review websites &#8211; and I\u2019m hoping to release it later this year. I was just working on a product review demo page where I\u2019ve uploaded an image of a MacBook Pro and I wanted to change the background color for the header of this product card.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"362\" src=\"https:\/\/joeyfarruggio.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/localhost_10108_wp-admin_post.php_post110actionedit-1024x362.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-607\" srcset=\"https:\/\/joeyfarruggio.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/localhost_10108_wp-admin_post.php_post110actionedit-1024x362.png 1024w, https:\/\/joeyfarruggio.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/localhost_10108_wp-admin_post.php_post110actionedit-300x106.png 300w, https:\/\/joeyfarruggio.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/localhost_10108_wp-admin_post.php_post110actionedit-768x271.png 768w, https:\/\/joeyfarruggio.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/localhost_10108_wp-admin_post.php_post110actionedit-1536x543.png 1536w, https:\/\/joeyfarruggio.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/localhost_10108_wp-admin_post.php_post110actionedit.png 1676w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>And I noticed how the image\u2019s white background doesn\u2019t look too great over the gray background.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Instead of bringing this image into photoshop, removing the background, and rey-loading it to the WordPress \u2013 what if I could take care of this right here in the Gutenerg editor?<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Well, we can\u2026 and with just a click of a button.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https:\/\/joeyfarruggio.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/image.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-608\" width=\"247\" height=\"183\" srcset=\"https:\/\/joeyfarruggio.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/image.png 558w, https:\/\/joeyfarruggio.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/image-300x223.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 247px) 100vw, 247px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The screenshot above shows an ACF field that adds one line of CSS to the image.<br>This is a pure CSS solution and it works in most modern browsers. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<pre><code lang=\"css\" class=\"language-css\">mix-blend-mode: multiply;<\/code><\/pre>\n\n\n\n<p>This feature works best when the background color is light shade\u2026 and fails completely if you go too dark.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Once you get your hands on this theme you can easily test it and see how it works in your own use case.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"698\" src=\"https:\/\/joeyfarruggio.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/remove-white-background-1024x698.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-613\" srcset=\"https:\/\/joeyfarruggio.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/remove-white-background-1024x698.png 1024w, https:\/\/joeyfarruggio.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/remove-white-background-300x204.png 300w, https:\/\/joeyfarruggio.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/remove-white-background-768x523.png 768w, https:\/\/joeyfarruggio.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/remove-white-background-1536x1046.png 1536w, https:\/\/joeyfarruggio.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/remove-white-background.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:100px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>So I&#8217;m building a premium WP theme tailored for Affiliates and product review websites &#8211; and I\u2019m hoping to release it later this year. I was just working on a product review demo page where I\u2019ve uploaded an image of a MacBook Pro and I wanted to change the background color for the header of [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[3],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/joeyfarruggio.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/606"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/joeyfarruggio.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/joeyfarruggio.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/joeyfarruggio.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/joeyfarruggio.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=606"}],"version-history":[{"count":5,"href":"https:\/\/joeyfarruggio.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/606\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":614,"href":"https:\/\/joeyfarruggio.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/606\/revisions\/614"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/joeyfarruggio.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=606"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/joeyfarruggio.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=606"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/joeyfarruggio.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=606"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}